    "text": "All right, Cody Jones,\nmoments away from going.",
    "start": 708.63,
    "duration": 2.31
  },
  {
    "text": "Talk to me.",
    "start": 710.94,
    "duration": 0.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Not scared, not fearful.",
    "start": 711.51,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "I think she's the best\nthat can make it happen.",
    "start": 712.86,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I've added fins last minute.",
    "start": 714.88,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "Zip tie or die baby.",
    "start": 716.49,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Good luck, Cody Jones.",
    "start": 718.02,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 721.08,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "And the timer starts now.",
    "start": 722.52,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "[HORN]",
    "start": 724.08,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "He's moving.",
    "start": 725.73,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not even going to lie.",
    "start": 726.23,
    "duration": 1.083
  },
  {
    "text": "Going so fast.",
    "start": 727.313,
    "duration": 2.067
  },
  {
    "text": "His first real test happens now.",
    "start": 729.38,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL]",
    "start": 731.22,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We're past it.",
    "start": 731.72,
    "duration": 0.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Checkpoint number one.",
    "start": 732.45,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh this is a winning machine.",
    "start": 734.39,
    "duration": 1.57
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Wicked magic\nevery day that I got.",
    "start": 735.96,
    "duration": 2.285
  },
  {
    "text": "Here comes the dish washer.",
    "start": 738.245,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh he ate a big wave.",
    "start": 743.38,
    "duration": 4.29
  },
  {
    "text": "He's past checkpoint two.",
    "start": 747.67,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants it.",
    "start": 750.67,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 751.83,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "You can hear the\npassion from here.",
    "start": 753.18,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants it.",
    "start": 754.95,
    "duration": 0.67
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) The future is golden.",
    "start": 755.62,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "The future--",
    "start": 758.76,
    "duration": 0.945
  },
  {
    "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
    "start": 761.272,
    "duration": 2.358
  },
  {
    "text": "He hung on.",
    "start": 763.63,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "A perfect run!",
    "start": 765.19,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL]",
    "start": 766.6,
    "duration": 3.91
  },
  {
    "text": "A perfect run.",
    "start": 770.51,
    "duration": 1.79
  },
  {
    "text": "2021 baby.",
    "start": 772.3,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, what a day.",
    "start": 773.65,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey we got an injury.",
    "start": 774.82,
    "duration": 2.15
  },
  {
    "text": "That's when I got cocky,\nstood up, took a tumble.",
    "start": 776.97,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Me on the concrete.",
    "start": 779.74,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude, would you like to\nguess your incredible time?",
    "start": 780.55,
    "duration": 2.125
  },
  {
    "text": "I actually would\nlike to just hear it.",
    "start": 782.675,
    "duration": 1.745
  },
  {
    "text": "1:15.",
    "start": 784.42,
    "duration": 1.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 785.93,
    "duration": 0.59
  },
  {
    "text": "No one got hurt.",
    "start": 786.52,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "We had a blast.",
    "start": 787.42,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's head to the outro.",
    "start": 788.98,
    "duration": 1.207
  },
  {
    "text": "First thing's first.",
    "start": 790.187,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Codes, congratulations.",
    "start": 791.02,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, it felt good.",
    "start": 793.0,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, next time if I would\nhave built the raft I",
    "start": 793.75,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "think I would've had it.",
    "start": 795.25,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, so close.",
    "start": 796.25,
    "duration": 0.838
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching guys.",
    "start": 797.088,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "You want to see our last\nvideo, click right over here.",
    "start": 798.13,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "If you want to follow us on Tik\nTok, got some great content.",
    "start": 799.84,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Click down here.",
    "start": 802.51,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Signing off for now.",
    "start": 803.65,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Pound it.",
    "start": 804.61,
    "duration": 0.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Noggin.",
    "start": 805.18,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "See ya.",
    "start": 805.81,
    "duration": 1.55
  }
